Pre-Game Insights: Team India is on the top of the ICC T20 Group 2 points table with 4 points after winning two matches - against Pakistan and the Netherlands.
The men in blue seem to be in good form and are now all set to play their next match against South Africa on 30 October 2022.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The India Vs South Africa T20 match will be played on Sunday, 30 October 2022 at Optus Stadium, Australia.
The live telecast of India vs South Africa T20 will be available on Star Sports Network. Viewers can also enjoy the live streaming on the Disney+ Hotstar app.
